The following sample configuration files should be present in this
archive:

mrc-asm.cfg                   ArrowSoft assembler/MrLink config (default)
mrc-masm.cfg                  MASM/MicroSoft Link config
mrc-tasm.cfg                  TASM/Turbo Link config
mrc-a86.cfg                   A86 assembler config

Select the appropriate config file for your preferred assembler, place
it into the same directory as MRC.EXE, and rename the file to MRC.CFG.

Use MRC-ASM.CFG if you do not have an assembler already installed.
